          "settings": {
            "title": "Product Dimensions",
            "content": "<p><strong>Size - 6.5ft Wide :<br/></strong>Frame Dimensions : 6.5ft wide x 7.5ft height<br/>Graphics Dimension : 80 inch wide x 90 inch height<br/>Package Dimension : 10 inch x 10 inch x 30 inch<br/>Package Weight : 10.6lbs</p><p><strong>Size - 8ft Wide :<br/></strong>Frame Dimensions : 8ft wide x 7.5ft height<br/>Graphics Dimension : 96 inch wide x 90 inch height<br/>Package Dimension : 10 inch x 10 inch x 30 inch<br/>Package Weight : 11.6lbs</p><p><strong>Size - 10ft Wide :</strong><br/>Frame Dimensions : 9.8ft wide x 7.5ft height<br/>Graphics Dimension : 115 inch wide x 90 inch height<br/>Package Dimension : 10 inch x 10 inch x 30 inch<br/>Package Weight : 16.5lbs</p><p><strong>Size - 13.2ft Wide :</strong><br/>Frame Dimensions : 13.2ft wide x 7.5ft height<br/>Graphics Dimension : 157 inch wide x 90 inch height<br/>Package Dimension : 15 inch x 15 inch x 30 inch<br/>Package Weight : 21lbs</p><p><strong>Size - 16.4ft Wide :</strong><br/>Frame Dimensions : 16.4ft wide x 7.5ft height<br/>Graphics Dimension : 197 inch wide x 90 inch height<br/>Package Dimension : 15 inch x 15 inch x 30 inch<br/>Package Weight : 23lbs</p><p><strong>Size - 20ft Wide :</strong><br/>Frame Dimensions : 19.5ft wide x 7.5ft height<br/>Graphics Dimension : 235 inch wide x 90 inch height<br/>Package Dimension : 15 inch x 15 inch x 30 inch<br/>Package Weight : 24lbs</p>"
